{"tid":2199638,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Nikola遭做空，Hindenburg Research：是一個錯綜複雜的騙局！","createTime":"2020-09-12T11:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T13:11:25.000Z","uid":295230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"16c4b5a6587c9501326c8d48026c38a9168dd39b","tid":2199638,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:08:26.000Z","msg":"9月10日，沽空機構Hindenburg Research發佈電動卡車製造商Nikola&nbsp;Corp (NASDAQ:NKLA)的做空報告。<br />\n<br />\nHindenburg Research在報告中揭示了爲什麼他們相信Nikola是一個錯綜複雜的騙局，其建立在其創始人和執行董事長特雷弗&middot;米爾頓(Trevor Milton)職業生涯中的幾十個謊言之上。<br />\n<br />\n消息公佈後，Nikola股價迅速下跌，截至北京時間22:22，該股跌3.87%，報40.73美元。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">通過包括電話錄音、短信、私人電子郵件和幕後照片的大量證據，Hindenburg Research認爲公司在其半掛式卡車、電池技術、氫氣生產、Nikola One甚至其數十億美元大訂單等諸多方面存在數十個虛假聲明。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nHindenburg Research稱，其創始人將這些虛假聲明轉化爲一家市值約200億美元的上市公司，通過謊稱擁有大量專利技術來誤導合作伙伴簽署協議。他與世界上一些頂尖的汽車公司簽訂了合作協議，這些公司都急於追趕特斯拉(<a href=\"http://TSLA.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FTSLA.US&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9fyuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=1942ad1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">TSLA.US</a>)在電動汽車界的領導地位。該機構認爲Nikola的合作伙伴沒有做足功課。"},{"pid":"dd97b2f5c166594de3feaf5d51675fe9eb686d38","tid":2199638,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:11:43.000Z","msg":"幾睇好第二間tsla - nkla<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2199221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2199221</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ffa74b3d7366cdf5d63c84c4e3191d9c358132","tid":2199638,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:15:19.000Z","msg":"NKLA股東打氣區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條on9仔又要家破人亡多次啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c74762361b3607e60ede3433b15801dc0aec681","tid":2199638,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:15:25.000Z","msg":"當gm傻仔咩 一於重倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795cac70e536252cb244c98fc2ee3b998ac1e8fb","tid":2199638,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買咗果d星期一不問價...呀唔係，係立即去IFC攞籌吧啦"},{"pid":"2c02e09c75f27f69e1b629ad92a27b1dd8f12899","tid":2199638,"uid":213268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795cac70e536252cb244c98fc2ee3b998ac1e8fb","tid":2199638,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買咗果d星期一不問價...呀唔係，係立即去IFC攞籌吧啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:17:00.000Z","msg":"不問價開put<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7bcdb39234e4fad2c85e7af07c2ee6ef7252d8","tid":2199638,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"做空機構：Nikola 為精心策畫騙局，盤中股價瀉 13%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做空機構 Hindenburg Research 宣稱，譽為「卡車界特斯拉」的 Nikola 車廠是場精心策畫的騙局，Nikola 大吹牛皮，騙到和通用汽車（GM）合作的機會，消息傳出後，Nikola 股價狂瀉。<br />\n<br />\n10 日 Nikola 重挫 11.33% 收 37.57 美元，盤中跌幅一度達 13%。本月 8 日 Nikola 宣布和 GM 結盟，股價狂飆 40.79%。<br />\n<br />\nBusiness Insider、Fox Business 報導，Hindenburg 10 日報告稱：「我們相信 Nikola 是錯綜複雜的詐騙案，建立在創辦人兼執行董事長 Trevor Milton 職業生涯的數十個謊言之上。」Hindenburg 引述電話、簡訊、照片為佐證，指控「<strong><span class=\"red\">我們從未見過上市公司進行此種程度的欺瞞，特別規模如此之大。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nHindenburg 表示，去年 Nikola 宣布要收購顛覆業界的公司，未來生產的鋰電池，重量和成本都不到對手一半。但此併購並未成真，後來 Nikola 發現電池科技只是概念。可是 <strong><span class=\"red\">Nikola 沒有收回此說法，Milton 仍到處吹噓</span></strong>。Hindenburg 指控 Nikola 從事多種詐欺行徑，如誇大旗下電動卡車的技術、灌水訂單數量，<strong><span class=\"red\">他們認為 Nikola 合夥人沒做功課，才會和 Nikola 合作。此處的合夥人應該是指 GM。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGM慘慘豬"},{"pid":"e9c5e2fbb375911c25779337f01aa4b81c25bc6e","tid":2199638,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c74762361b3607e60ede3433b15801dc0aec681","tid":2199638,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:15:25.000Z","msg":"當gm傻仔咩 一於重倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:19:54.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69196eaaef65c796c800bb68f83c7c0e3da576e","tid":2199638,"uid":120499,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T11:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n21Natb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn21Natb.png&h=02562cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經有Intitution同Trade 低價掃緊貨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有on9 以為NKLA佢會跌到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so